ASST. BUSINESS MANAGER – ID CARDS & ACCESS CONTROL SYSTEMS
Reports to Marketing Manager of the department. Should have previous experience in planning, pricing, negotiation, marketing, exhibitions etc. for ID Cards and Access Control Systems solution division. Able to develop business in the UAE and neighboring countries. Co-ordinate with service engineers. Engineering qualified with previous experience in the same industry in the UAE is required. Good knowledge of the local market. Arabic an added advantage. Should have valid UAE driving license. Salary range 5300 to 5500 USD.
